text: Richard Doey (born 27 December 1956) is a Canadian rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chatham-Kent
